history.content: Join us, Sunday April 11th at 3pm PST, in introducing SAGB’s first Women in Sports Analytics Panel! As part of our diversity and inclusivity mission, we will be welcoming some of the top female analytics executives from around the sports world. Emmalee Dolfi from the Tampa Bay Rays, Sarah Bailey from the LA Rams and Kanitha Mann from the NBA will all be with us discussing their careers and the challenges they faced in a predominantly male dominated industry. This panel will be open to all that are interested. Hope to see you there! Link to register for the zoom tinyurl.com/kbdrnh4r
history.subject: Women in Sports Analytics Panel Happening this Sunday!
